data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Seller offering $5000 toward closing costs!! 2.79% ASSUMABLE VA LOAN!! Warm and welcoming, this residence features a smart layout with tons of attractive additions. First, be greeted by the stained concrete floors and spacious living room with custom built entertainment center that lends seamlessly to the kitchen. Featuring an open concept design, beautiful granite counters, breakfast bar, eat in-dining area and gas range, this kitchen offers ample storage and counter space making entertaining a breeze. The secondary bathroom comes complete with two entrances for added privacy and accessibility from the front bedroom. Located at the back of the home, is the large master suite including a huge walk-in closet and private ensuite with dual vanity, garden tub and separate shower. The laundry closet has been tastefully updated with beadboard and cabinetry for additional storage. Even the garage is more functional with added cabinetry and counter space. Outback, be pleased by the covered porch, massive deck and pergola allowing for plenty of room for seating plus a bar area making this the perfect setting for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Retaining walls already in place for a pool, trampoline or whatever your heart desires. Home is less than a block away from neighborhood access to Science Hall Elementary, plus tons of shopping, eateries and Seton Hospital just around the corner! Storage shed and water softener to convey!
